    <string name="acknowledgement">Acknowledgement</string>
    <string name="acknowledgement_desc">The developers would like to express their deepest gratitude to Ma\'am Norianne Lamadrid, their dedicated instructor, for her invaluable guidance, patience, and professional expertise throughout this course. Her insights and mentorship played a crucial role in the conceptualization and realization of the CCMS Archive. \n\nThe developers also extend their thanks to the CCMS Faculty for providing an environment that encourages innovation and shared learning. This project would not have been possible without their continuous support.</string>

